  "date": "2025-06-23 02:44:00",
  "author": "天空之城城主",
  "siteName": "Web3天空之城",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"Web3天空之城\" data-alias=\"Web3SkyCity\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/V08icaMk7MVbppLs8UnGYAUOJELEkxfo0QxOGhP1zvKpjV4X5c6nHQibuV79E4RgCqQeP4VDEAeiaPeQ6wI5QWRHQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"美好的，有趣的，值得铭记的\" data-id=\"MzIxODUzNTg2MA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: none;height: 1px;color: inherit;margin: 0px 0px 2em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Web3天空之城·城主</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为YC的前掌门也是最著名的一任掌门， OpenAI CEO Sam Altman近日回到了YC的创业学院峰会，和现任YC掌门Garry Tan在面向全球顶尖初创企业创始人的闭门分享中，Sam系统性地剖析了他从启动OpenAI到构想通用人工智能（AGI）未来的十年心路。他详细阐述了初创企业如何在AI巨头的阴影下构建独特的护城河，人机交互的终极形态将如何“融化”现有界面，以及为何当下的混乱与不确定性，恰恰构成了“</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">有史以来最好的创业时机</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">”。</span></p>\n   <section class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <mp-common-videosnap class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_iframe videosnap_video_iframe videosnap_video_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpvideosnap\" data-url=\"https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=rjD5jyTuFrIpZ2ibE8T7YmwgiahniaXswqzt3x3Ciab8UkGPsicmdnzAfiaAE8lUwxK7MCfwvSH0mW812Ut82GCtIBzoRuQ10MT2KZYbH1D0OeAj284ib6Nl5htwA&amp;token=2lt8WBSnjTlxibCQZrake2TFpnm5tgGvD3Fbp02fnu8qcfK5xG73R55h9OEJJLQjKsPPofWxwanSA5enHlUdmcpGtGA8qibQbJ38DGMJs33f7GGbLglGsP2pW0RmnjlKCuSibHPltwIZBnDSBzDwYiaOG7Vs8rNCczsiaibYmwUWZWaTE&amp;idx=1&amp;hy=SH&amp;m=&amp;scene=2&amp;uzid=1\" data-headimgurl=\"http://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/OxUBpiaYgpHghKXFOmQ9a9fftKuicVaxBluk3GuiaRRlAZNSS7D0zxbYxWkOal34xcUKrjTNdBwJ1Q/0\" data-username=\"v2_060000231003b20faec8c4e38a19cbd7c902ed32b0773f579304e9c89386b01234df74bfd579@finder\" data-nickname=\"第3新天空之城\" data-desc=\"奥特曼YC峰会谈OpenAI未来, ChatGPT起源及AI硬件 #英语听力\n#英语口语\n#奥特曼\n#AI未来\n#创业历程\n\n\" data-nonceid=\"1236185895993069162\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-type=\"video\" data-id=\"export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAAarYAT2Yd-QAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPE_6c8HE0FFYOIzNPgMIua7__yFoCWpsvr4Rlaysrc\"></mp-common-videosnap>\n   </section>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心观点精粹</span></strong></h3>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">关于创业时机</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“这是有史以来，在技术史上，最好的创业时期，永远都是。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">关于宏大愿景</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们说，好吧，我们要朝着通用人工智能（AGI）努力。世界上百分之九十九的人认为我们疯了。那百分之一的人里有很多聪明人，而且他们无处可去。我们能够真正集中人才。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">关于创业建议</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们希望成为一个让其他人构建东西的平台。我们的建议是，不要构建我们的核心聊天助手。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">关于个人赋能</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“一个拥有大量能动性的个人或一小群人能够完成多少事情，将是未来10年最明显的变化之一。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">关于未来交互</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“科幻小说正确地描述了一件事，那就是界面几乎消失了……那将会是一个几乎融化的界面。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">关于人才招聘</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“雇佣看斜率，而不是Y轴截距。我认为这简直是不可思议的好建议。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-size:17px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;border-width:0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">关于长期信念</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“美好的部分非常美好，比你想象的还要好。而困难的部分简直令人震惊地更加困难……你必须坚持下去。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: none;height: 1px;color: inherit;margin: 2em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一、源起：一个近乎疯狂的赌注</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">回望OpenAI创立之初的2015年，Sam Altman坦言，那是一个与今天截然不同的世界。当时，</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“通用人工智能（AGI）听起来很疯狂”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，而DeepMind似乎已遥遥领先。启动OpenAI的决定并非显而易见，而是经过长达一年的激烈讨论，最终</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">就像抛硬币一样，胜负难料</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">然而，正是这个看似不可能的宏大愿景，成为了吸引顶尖人才的磁石。Altman强调，如果你选择做一件与众不同的事，即使成功率看似渺茫，但其巨大的潜在价值会吸引那些同样怀有疯狂梦想的精英。</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们说，好吧，我们要争取通用人工智能（AGI）。世界上百分之九十九的人认为我们疯了。世界上百分之一的人真正产生了共鸣。结果发现，那百分之一的人里有很多聪明人，而且他们无处可去。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这种独特的使命感，让OpenAI在早期就形成了强大的人才密度，这是任何试图模仿主流路径的公司都难以企及的优势。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">二、未来已来：个性化AI与“融化”的界面</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于AI的未来形态，Altman的构想早已超越了简单的问答式聊天机器人。他认为，我们正走向一个</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">个性化AI</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的时代。他将“记忆”功能视为今年最重要的发布，因为它预示着一个全新的产品方向：</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“你将拥有一个了解你的实体，它连接到你所有的东西，并主动帮助你。它不会只是像你发送一条消息，它给你回复一条，而是它会一直运行。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个持续运行的AI伙伴，将彻底改变我们与计算机的交互方式。Altman预言，未来的界面将不再是我们今天所见的布满图标和通知的屏幕，而是会</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">几乎融化消失</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。他与苹果传奇设计师Jony Ive的合作，正是为了探索这种全新的交互范式。</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“当今的语音界面很糟糕，因为它们效果不好。但理论上，如果你能对电脑说，‘这就是我今天想要发生的事情’……它就只是完成了所有事情。而且你信任它能正常运作。那将会是一个几乎融化的界面。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这意味着，计算机将从一个需要我们主动操作的工具，变为一个无缝融入生活、能预判我们需求并自主行动的智能伙伴。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">三、技术路线图：从GPT-5到机器人时代</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当被问及GPT-5及更长远的技术愿景时，Altman描绘了一幅多模态能力与深度推理能力完全融合的图景。未来的模型将不仅仅是文本生成器，而是能够</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在需要时进行非常深入的推理，并在需要时生成像实时视频一样的东西</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。这意味着，你可以让AI进行深度研究，为你编写一个全新的定制化应用，甚至实时渲染可交互的视频。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一步，是通往</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">具身智能</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的关键。Altman对此充满期待：</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们的策略一直是先攻克（认知）这一点，然后确保我们可以将其连接到机器人。但机器人的时代即将到来。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他甚至大胆畅想，</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“当你注册像ChatGPT最高级的订阅服务时，我们会免费赠送你一个人形机器人。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这背后是他对物理世界自动化的深刻思考：一旦拥有了足够智能的“大脑”，通过机器人自动化整个供应链——从采矿、运输到制造新的机器人——人类社会将迎来前所未有的物质富足。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">四、创始人必修课：在AI时代构建防御性</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于所有身处AI浪潮中的创业者，Altman给出了最核心、最直接的建议：</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不要试图去复制基础模型</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。他坦言：</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“当人们说，‘我要创办一家新的初创公司，我要做一个ChatGPT的版本’时，我们会感到难过，因为我们认为我们能把这件事做得很好。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">真正的机会在于利用OpenAI这样的平台，去探索尚未被满足的广阔市场。他强调，</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“初创公司获胜的方式是，它们能够比大公司更快地迭代，并且能够以更低的成本做到这一点。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;AI带来的剧烈变革，恰恰为初创公司提供了以小博大的黄金窗口。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么，防御性究竟是什么？Altman认为，关键在于</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">独特性</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“如果每个人都在尝试做同样的事情，就很难构建出有防御性的东西……最好、最持久的公司通常不会做和别人一样的事情。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这种独特性让你赢得了宝贵的时间窗口，在竞争对手涌入之前，去打磨产品、建立品牌，并找到真正的护城河——无论是独特的网络效应、数据优势，还是像OpenAI的“记忆”功能一样，深度绑定用户的个性化体验。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">五、领导力核心：招聘看“斜率”，而非“截距”</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在如何聚集人才方面，Altman分享了他从YC时期就坚持的理念。他从不看重光鲜的履历，比如在哪家大公司工作或毕业于哪所名校。他关注的是候选人</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">做过的最令人印象深刻的事情是什么</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">他引用YC联合创始人Paul Buchheit的名言，总结了自己的招聘哲学：</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">雇佣看斜率，而不是Y轴截距。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;换言之，一个人的成长潜力（斜率）远比他当前的成就（Y轴截距）更重要。他建议创始人优先选择</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">年轻、有干劲、但显然能把事情做好的人</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，而不是经验丰富但可能已经失去冲劲的资深管理者。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">六、创业者的心态：在漫长的逆境中保持信念</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Altman毫不讳言创业的残酷性。他分享了早期收到偶像Elon Musk的邮件，被告知OpenAI成功率为零的经历。</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我记得那天晚上回家，心想，‘如果他是对的呢？’……面对很多人告诉你你错了，很难有信念。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">他认为，创业就像抚养孩子：</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“美好的部分非常美好，比你想象的还要好。而困难的部分简直令人震惊地更加困难，没有人能用一种对你来说有意义的方式来表达。你必须坚持下去。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;对创始人而言，最重要的品质之一，就是在这种漫长的、消耗心力的逆境中，学会相信自己的直觉，并保持长期的信念和韧性。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">七、终极愿景：用AI加速科学，创造彻底的富足</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在访谈的最后，Altman揭示了他内心深处的终极驱动力：将人工智能应用于科学发现。他坚信，</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“世界上所有长期可持续的经济增长……基本上都是发现新的科学。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;如果能用AI大幅加速科学发现的进程，人类社会将迎来难以想象的繁荣。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这解释了他为何同时对AI和能源（如他投资的核聚变公司Helion）抱有近乎痴迷的热情。在他看来，</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">智能</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">和</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">能源</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">是通往</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">彻底富足</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">未来的两大技术杠杆。一个由强大AI工具赋能的个人或小团队，将能完成过去需要庞大组织才能企及的宏伟事业，而廉价、丰富的能源则是这一切的物质基础。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当被问及对现场创始人的最终寄语时，他以一种不容置疑的乐观，为这个充满不确定性的时代定下基调：</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“这是有史以来，在技术史上，最好的创业时期，永远都是。”</span></strong></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;font-weight:bold;padding-left:12px;font-size:20.4px;border-color:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);line-height:2.4em;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);border-width:1px 1px 1px 4px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:inherit;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">访谈全文传送</span></h3>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <section>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODUzNTg2MA==&amp;mid=2247488618&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=267219bc4973aa101c42271b4f0a7d59&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【全文版】OpenAI奥特曼 YC新老掌门人访谈：构建AGI未来与下一代初创企业 |1.5万字+视频\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【全文版】OpenAI奥特曼 YC新老掌门人访谈：构建AGI未来与下一代初创企业 |1.5万字+视频</a></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Sam Altman 分享 AI 时代创业七堂课，涵盖 AGI 愿景、未来交互、招聘及创始人必修课。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Sam Altman 分享 AI 时代创业七堂课，涵盖 AGI 愿景、未来交互、招聘及创始人必修课。",
  "summary": "文章总结了 OpenAI CEO Sam Altman 在 YC 创业学院峰会上的核心分享。Altman 回顾了 OpenAI 成立之初的“疯狂”赌注，强调宏大愿景对吸引顶尖人才的重要性。他展望了 AI 的未来形态，认为个性化 AI 将带来“融化”的界面，彻底改变人机交互。技术路线上，他提及 GPT-5 将融合多模态和深度推理能力，并预言机器人时代即将到来。对于创业者，他建议不要复制基础模型，而应利用平台构建独特性，以迭代速度取胜。在招聘方面，他强调应看重候选人的成长潜力（斜率）。最后，他分享了创业的艰辛与保持长期信念的重要性，并表达了用 AI 加速科学、实现物质富足的终极愿景。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "抓住当下是 AI 时代创业的最佳时机",
      "explanation": "AI 巨变带来前所未有的机遇，初创公司凭借快速迭代和低成本优势，能在大公司阴影下找到突破口，构建独特护城河。"
    },
    {
      "point": "宏大愿景是吸引顶尖人才的关键",
      "explanation": "选择一个看似疯狂但有巨大潜在价值的愿景（如追求 AGI），能够吸引到最聪明、最有共同使命感的人才。"
    },
    {
